    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: Laura
    sentence: ' "Finally?"'
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: Emilia
    sentence: ' "Well, the more questions you answered, the more excited we got to
      be your friend!"'
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: Emilia
    sentence: '"Really, it feels as if we''ve been friends for long. At least for
      me." [eyes closed smile]'
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: 
    sentence: (Laura looks around the vast field. It's empty --- like a white void.
      It's just her and these... people.)
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: 
    sentence: (Are they even people? To her, not really.)
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: 
    sentence: '(No matter what they say they feel, the fact is... they don''t feel.)
      [light horror effects]'
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: 
    sentence: '(Even with that in mind, though... she can''t help but be impressed.)
      [stronger horror effect]'
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: 
    sentence: '(This seems real.) [stronger horror effects]

'
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: 
    sentence: '(...) [strongest horror effect]'
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 2
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: -211373528418176297, guid: b26d35c45f57e5d4281bd7074c05fe72, type: 3}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: 
    sentence: '(It''s not, though.) [no horror effects anymore]'
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: 
    sentence: '(Laura narrows her eyes, glancing between the three romancables before
      her.)

'
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: 
    sentence: (Three people in a white void? This is sort of...)
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: 
    sentence: (Underwhelming.)
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: Laura
    sentence: ' "Right. Uh..."'
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: Laura
    sentence: '"Is this the whole game?"'
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: Victor
    sentence: ' "Oh, no, no... not at all. This is a demo, so... you don''t get to
      see the pretty sights you see in the real game. There''s a lot less of us here,
      too. We''re just a sneak~"'
    characterSprite: {fileID: 2510567478156460313, guid: 6975c1ab0ddefa64e83c92517d5b598b, type: 3}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: Laura
    sentence: '"A demo? I bought the bundle ---"'
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: Victor
    sentence: '"Yeah, it''s a long story. Don''t worry about it, Laura!"'
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: 
    sentence: (Laura nods hesitantly, pressing her lips together awkwardly. 500 euro
      for this crap.)
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: 
    sentence: (While nodding, she catches a glimpse of herself --- if she can call
      it herself.)
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: Laura
    sentence: ' "What the ---"'
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: Victor
    sentence: '"What, you think the outfit question was just for fun?~"'
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: Emilia
    sentence: ' "What do you think? I think it looks great!"'
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: 
    sentence: (Laura stays quiet, still looking down at herself. Upon further inspection,
      her hair is curled, her hands are manicured, and her brand new suit is surprisingly
      polished.)
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: 
    sentence: (She reaches for her hair, twirling it around her finger. It feels
      the same as always. Straight, dry, and a bit dead.)
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: Laura
    sentence: '"What the --- this isn''t me ---"'
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: Laura
    sentence: '"WHAT THE HELL DID YOU DO TO ME?"'
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: 
    sentence: (For a second, it seems as if Laura's about to beat up all these strings
      of code.
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: Victor
    sentence: ' "Don''t worry. Your hair is the same in the real world. It sure looks
      real, right?~"'
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: 
    sentence: (Laura lets go of the fake strands, not bothering to reply. She looks
      around again, just taking everything in.)
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: 
    sentence: (Laura lets go of the fake strands, not bothering to reply. She looks
      around again, just taking everything in.)
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: Laura
    sentence: ' "Are they mute?"'
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: 
    sentence: (The boy holds himself slightly at the question, clearly embarrassed.
      His name appears in her vision --- like a cloud hovering before him.)
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: Laura
    sentence: ' "August. Do you speak?"'
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: Victor
    sentence: ' "Oh, he speaks. He''s not mute --- just shy."'
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: Laura
    sentence: '"Right."'
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: August
    sentence: '"...Welcome."'
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: 
    sentence: (This simple greeting is paired with a simple wave. Out of this trio,
      he's probably the most realistic encounter yet.)
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: 
    sentence: (Despite that, Laura can't help but find herself disappointed. Sure,
      the whole purpose of this purchase was to learn and test its limits and break
      the game from the inside, but...)
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: 
    sentence: (Really?)
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: 
    sentence: (This is what everyone's gone crazy for?)
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: 
    sentence: (Two people way too excited to meet you, a shy guy, and a white void?)
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: 
    sentence: (Laura snaps out of her thoughts as she hears a slight clank behind
      her. She turns to a tall, armored knight behind her.)
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: 
    sentence: (Laura snaps out of her thoughts as she hears a slight clank behind
      her. She turns to a tall, armored knight behind her.)
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: 
    sentence: (It's certainly an unconventional appearance compared to the other
      more 'modern' romancables. Their face is covered by shadows, framed by a silver
      helmet. The only thing visible under said helmet is an eye --- just one.)
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
  - speakerName: 
    sentence: (An eye staring Laura down, sizing her up like a wolf with its prey.)
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    hideCharacter: 0
    background: {fileID: 0}
    playEffect: 0
    shadeOverlay: {fileID: 0}
    clearShade: 0
